data.description: Welcome to your oasis on Kildare Drive, nestled within the heart of the vibrant Banning Lewis Ranch community! As you step into this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, you'll feel the inviting embrace of modern comforts intertwined with the coziness of community living.    Sunlight floods the open living space, creating an atmosphere perfect for both relaxed evenings and lively gatherings that effortlessly extends into the gourmet kitchen—a space where culinary creations come to life and where memories are made around the breakfast bar.    Upstairs, your personal retreat awaits in the primary suite, boasting an en-suite bathroom featuring dual sinks and a spacious shower. Three additional bedrooms offer versatility for family, or guests.    The unfinished basement? It's your canvas, waiting for your vision—perhaps a home theater, a creative studio, or the ultimate hangout spot.    But it's not just about the home. Banning Lewis Ranch is your extended playground, offering parks, trails, and a community pool, all designed to complement your lifestyle. With nearby shops, dining, and entertainment, convenience and enjoyment are just steps away.
